The '''Hjort Fracture Zone''' ({{coord|62|S|163|E|source:GNIS|display=inline,title}}) is an undersea [[fracture zone]] in Antarctica. The name was approved by the [[Advisory Committee for Undersea Features]] in December 1971.<ref name=gnis/>

